trans-unit.source: Creates a Web.config file for a SOAP-enabled COM+ application and adds component entries to the file for COM interfaces being published in the application.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en Web.config-filen for en SOAP-aktiverte COM +-programmet og legger til komponenten oppføringer i filen for COM-grensesnitt som publiseres i applikasjonen.

trans-unit.source: The IServerWebConfig interface is implemented only by the <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.ServerWebConfig> class and is only used within the .NET Framework infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: Grensesnittet IServerWebConfig implementeres bare ved den <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.ServerWebConfig>klasse og brukes bare i .NET Framework-infrastruktur.</xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.ServerWebConfig>

trans-unit.source: Rather than implementing this interface or instantiating an IServerWebConfig interface object, use the <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.Publish> class, which implements the <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.IComSoapPublisher> interface.
trans-unit.target: I stedet for implementerer dette grensesnittet eller starte et IServerWebConfig grensesnittet objekt, bruker du <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.Publish>klasse som implementerer den <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.IComSoapPublisher>grensesnittet.</xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.IComSoapPublisher> </xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.Publish>

trans-unit.source: IServerWebConfig is used internally by the .NET Framework.
trans-unit.target: IServerWebConfig er brukt internt av .NET Framework.

trans-unit.source: You do not need to use it directly in your code.
trans-unit.target: Du trenger ikke å bruke den direkte i koden.

trans-unit.source: Adds XML elements to a Web.config file for a COM interface being published in a SOAP-enabled COM+ application.
trans-unit.target: Legger til XML-elementer i Web.config-filen for et COM-grensesnitt som er publisert i SOAP-aktiverte COM +-programmet.

trans-unit.source: See the <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.ServerWebConfig.AddElement%2A> method for implementation details.
trans-unit.target: Se den <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.ServerWebConfig.AddElement%2A>metode for implementeringsdetaljene.</xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.ServerWebConfig.AddElement%2A>

trans-unit.source: However, you do not need to call `AddElement` method directly.
trans-unit.target: Men du trenger ikke å kalle `AddElement` metoden direkte.

trans-unit.source: The path for the existing Web.config file.
trans-unit.target: Banen for den eksisterende Web.config-filen.

trans-unit.source: The name of the assembly that contains the type being added.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på samlingen som inneholder typen som legges til.

trans-unit.source: The name of the type being added.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på typen som legges til.

trans-unit.source: The programmatic identifier for the type being added.
trans-unit.target: Program-IDen for typen som legges til.

trans-unit.source: A string constant that corresponds to the name of a member from the <xref href="System.Runtime.Remoting.WellKnownObjectMode"></xref> enumeration, which indicates how a well-known object is activated.
trans-unit.target: En strengkonstant som tilsvarer navnet på et medlem fra den <xref href="System.Runtime.Remoting.WellKnownObjectMode"> </xref> opplisting som angir hvordan et kjent objekt er aktivert.

trans-unit.source: A string to which an error message can be written.
trans-unit.target: Du kan skrive en feilmelding som en streng.

trans-unit.source: Creates a Web.config file for a SOAP-enabled COM+ application so that the file is ready to have XML elements added for COM interfaces being published.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en Web.config-filen for en SOAP-aktiverte COM +-programmet slik at filen er klar til å ha XML-elementer som er lagt til for COM-grensesnitt publiseres.

trans-unit.source: See the <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.ServerWebConfig.Create%2A> method for implementation details.
trans-unit.target: Se den <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.ServerWebConfig.Create%2A>metode for implementeringsdetaljene.</xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.ServerWebConfig.Create%2A>

trans-unit.source: However, you do not need to call `Create` directly.
trans-unit.target: Men du trenger ikke å kalle `Create` direkte.

trans-unit.source: The folder in which to create the configuration file.
trans-unit.target: Mappen der du vil opprette konfigurasjonsfil.

trans-unit.source: The string value to which a config extension can be added (for example, Web for Web.config).
trans-unit.target: Strengverdien som filtypen config kan legges til (for eksempel Web for Web.config).

trans-unit.source: A string to which an error message can be written.
trans-unit.target: Du kan skrive en feilmelding som en streng.
